data.description:
Welcome to 110 Teal Bluff Boulevard!! Like new built in 2022.
 Over 2000 square feet
This lovely home offers 3 Bedrooms 2.5 Baths and a 2 car garage! The first floor includes the living area with a foyer / flex room currently used as an office. 
Open floor design kitchen comes with granite counters, separate island, dining area and livingroom.
Stove operates off of natural gas.
The upstairs you have a very spacious master bedroom with a double vanity private bath and walk in closet that is a one of a kind! Book today to see!!
